440752,104,1617,67,109,1,301,30,"‘‘ idaṃ cīvaraṃ anupubbena vaṇṇavikāratañceva jiṇṇabhāvañca upagantvā pādapuñchanacoḷakaṃ hutvā yaṭṭhikoṭiyā chaḍḍanīyaṃ bhavissati, sace panassa sāmiko bhaveyya, nāssa evaṃ vinassituṃ dadeyyā’’ ti evaṃ assāmikabhāvapaccavekkhaṇena ca,‘‘ anaddhaniyaṃ idaṃ tāvakālikan’’ ti evaṃ tāvakālikabhāvapaccavekkhaṇena cāti. "
