440754,104,1618,2,77,1,506,56,"{Sattasaṅkhārakelāyanapuggalaparivajjanatā}ti ettha yo puggalo gihi vā attano puttadhītādike, pabbajito vā attano antevāsikasamānupajjhāyakādike mamāyati, sahattheneva nesaṃ kesacchedanasūcikammacīvaradhovanarajanapattapacanādīni karoti, muhuttampi apassanto‘‘ asuko sāmaṇero kuhiṃ asuko daharo kuhin’’ ti bhantamigo viya ito cito ca oloketi, aññena kesacchedanādīnaṃ atthāya‘‘ muhuttaṃ asukaṃ pesethā’’ ti yāciyamānopi‘‘ amhepi taṃ attano kammaṃ na kārema, tumhe naṃ gahetvā kilamessathā’’ ti na deti, ayaṃ sattakelāyano nāma. "
