444291,105,559,2,50,1,429,42,"266. Iti bhagavā ettakena kathāmaggena evaṃ gahapatiputtassa ariyasāvako catūhi kāraṇehi akusalaṃ pahāya chahi kāraṇehi bhogānaṃ apāyamukhaṃ vajjetvā soḷasa mittāni sevanto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā dārabharaṇaṃ karonto dhammikena ājīvena jīvati, devamanussānañca antare aggikkhandho viya virocatīti vajjanīyadhammavajjanatthaṃ sevitabbadhammasevanatthañca ovādaṃ datvā idāni namassitabbā cha disā dassento kathañca {gahapatiputtā}tiādimāha. "
444292,105,560,2,24,1,140,16,"Tattha {chaddisāpaṭicchādī}ti yathā chahi disāhi āgamanabhayaṃ na āgacchati, khemaṃ hoti nibbhayaṃ evaṃ viharanto‘‘ chaddisāpaṭicchādī’’ ti vuccati."
