447449,106,149,27,57,1,141,22,"Dhammadinnā taṃ upadhāretvā,‘‘ ayyaputta, kasmā tvaṃ ajja mama hatthaṃ nālambi, bhuñjamānopi na kiñci kathesi, atthi nu kho koci mayhaṃ doso’’ ti āha. "
