449605,106,1659,158,172,1,50,8,"‘‘ Aññena me payojanaṃ natthi, tadeva pucchāmi, tātā’’ ti."
449606,106,1659,173,192,1,81,13,"‘‘ Amma, tvaṃ attano anācikkhituṃ na desi, ajja te sabbarattiṃ devo vassanto diṭṭho’’ ti?"
449607,106,1659,193,219,1,123,18,"‘‘ Diṭṭho me, tāta, mayhameva so sabbarattiṃ vuṭṭho, taṃ kāraṇaṃ pacchā kathessāmi, etasmiṃ tāva me seṭṭhigehe pavattiṃ kathehī’’ ti."
