449616,106,1663,40,59,1,157,17,"Satthā jetavane mahāparisāmajjhe nisīditvā dhammaṃ desento taṃ tathā paribbhamantiṃ disvā ñāṇaparipākañca oloketvā yathā vihārābhimukhī āgacchati, tathā akāsi. "
