449978,106,1895,43,52,1,41,5,‘‘ balakkārenapi deviṃ dasabalaṃ dassethā’’ ti. 
449979,106,1895,53,63,1,86,10,Devī vihāraṃ gantvā divasabhāgaṃ khepetvā nivattentī satthāraṃ adisvāva gantuṃ āraddhā. 
449980,106,1895,64,71,1,57,7,Atha naṃ rājapurisā anicchantimpi satthu santikaṃ nayiṃsu. 
