449982,106,1895,85,90,1,28,5,Khemā devī taṃ disvā cintesi–
449983,106,1895,91,120,1,206,23,"‘‘ evarūpā nāma devaccharapaṭibhāgā itthiyo bhagavato avidūre tiṭṭhanti, ahaṃ etāsaṃ paricārikatāyapi nappahomi, manampi nikkāraṇā pāpacittassa vasena naṭṭhā’’ ti nimittaṃ gahetvā tameva itthiṃ olokayamānā aṭṭhāsi. "
